<p><strong>合著人员：</strong><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluecat-error" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4432653); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4432653&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720549" alt="Bluecat Error" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4432653)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluecat-error" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4432653); return false;">Bluecat Error</a></span><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/misaka19092nd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3242622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720549" alt="Misaka19092nd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3242622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/misaka19092nd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242622); return false;">Misaka19092nd</a></span></p>
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
